<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ title }}</title>
    <meta name="description" content="{{ description }}">
    <meta name="keywords" content="공모주, IPO, 청약, 주식, 캘린더, 일정">
    <link rel="canonical" href="{{ site_url }}">
    <meta property="og:title" content="{{ title }}">
    <meta property="og:description" content="{{ description }}">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:url" content="{{ site_url }}">
    <meta property="og:locale" content="ko_KR">
    <meta property="og:image" content="{{ og_image_url }}">
    
    <link rel="manifest" href="manifest.json">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0066cc">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="icon-192.png">

    <!-- Twitter Card -->
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="{{ title }}">
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="{{ description }}">
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="{{ og_image_url }}">

    <script type="application/ld+json">
        {{ structured_data | safe }}
    </script>
    <!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->
    <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id={{ ga_id }}"></script>
    <script>
      window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
      function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
      gtag('js', new Date());
      gtag('config', '{{ ga_id }}');
    </script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Google AdSense -->
    <script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client={{ adsense_client_id }}"
     crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>공모주 캘린더</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">대한민국 IPO 청약 일정</p>
        </header>


        <div class="ad-banner" role="region" aria-label="광고">
            <!-- gong-mo -->
            <ins class="adsbygoogle"
                 style="display:block"
                 data-ad-client="{{ adsense_client_id }}"
                 data-ad-slot="{{ adsense_slot_top }}"
                 data-ad-format="auto"
                 data-full-width-responsive="false"></ins>
            <script>
                 (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
            </script>
        </div>

        <section class="calendar-section">
            <iframe src="{{ calendar_embed_url }}"
                    title="공모주 구글 캘린더"
                    width="100%"
                    height="600">
            </iframe>
            <section class="subscribe-section">
                <div class="button-group">
                    <a href="{{ calendar_subscribe_url }}"
                       class="subscribe-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                        + Google 캘린더에 추가
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="update-info update-info--text">
                    <span class="label">마지막 업데이트:</span>
                    <span id="last-updated">-</span>
                </div>
            </section>
        </section>

        </section>


        <section class="ipo-list-section">
            <h2>청약 일정 목록</h2>
            <div class="filter-controls" id="filter-controls">
                <button class="filter-btn active" data-filter="upcoming">다가오는 일정</button>
                <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="all">전체</button>
            </div>
            <div id="ipo-list" class="ipo-list">
                <p class="loading">데이터를 불러오는 중...</p>
                <!-- 인피드 광고 영역 (5번째 항목 위치) -->
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer>
        <div class="ad-banner-bottom" role="region" aria-label="광고">
            <!-- gong-mo-bottom -->
            <ins class="adsbygoogle"
                 style="display:block"
                 data-ad-client="{{ adsense_client_id }}"
                 data-ad-slot="{{ adsense_slot_bottom }}"
                 data-ad-format="auto"
                 data-full-width-responsive="false"></ins>
            <script>
                 (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
            </script>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links">
            데이터를 가져온 <a href="http://www.38.co.kr" class="footer-source-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">38커뮤니케이션 바로가기</a>
            <p class="footer-disclaimer">본 서비스는 38커뮤니케이션과는 별개로 운영되는 서비스입니다.</p>
        </div>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script src="app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
